# This specification defines a 32-bit adder using word-level arithmetic operations.
# It serves as the "golden reference" for verifying the structural implementation.
#
# Its logical equivalence to the structural (ripple-carry) specification will be formally
# proven in `proofs/prove_adder32_equivalence.tau`.
