# Inputs:
#   a31..a0: 32-bit input vector A
#   b31..b0: 32-bit input vector B
#   cin:     1-bit carry-in
#
# Outputs:
#   s31..s0:  32-bit sum vector S
#   cout:     1-bit final carry-out

